race.comment: BLUE JUGGLER (1) was below best last time at this track (22.72) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length fifth. Has already won two times from this draw. Looks a key chance on best form. SHERRY NOT BERRY (7) was unfancied latest when jumping from this same draw but belied the odds to place (22.55) over 400m at this track in a Grade 4/5. Has the ability and can measure up. AUSSIE RATTLER (2) had been racing in honest fashion recording two placings in a row before finishing sixth (23.63) at Richmond latest. Solid record here at the distance winning six races. Expected to run well. MARSHALL KADE (6) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.
